\[
[x,H] = \frac{1}{2m}[x,p^2] = \frac{1}{2m}(p[x,p] + [x,p]p).
\]


To be consistent with linearity and locality, we require


\[
[x,p] = i\hbar,
\]


which yields the standard quantum commutation relation.
\end{proof}

